com.facebook.buck.rules.keys.hasher

Class ForwardingRuleKeyHasher<HASH,HASH2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.keys.hasher.ForwardingRuleKeyHasher<HASH,HASH2>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RuleKeyHasher<HASH>

    public abstract class ForwardingRuleKeyHasher<HASH,HASH2>
extends Object
implements RuleKeyHasher<HASH>
    A RuleKeyHasher that forwards all the methods to the two underlying hashers.

    hash() invokes the method of the both underlying hashers and returns the hash of the first one.
